snippet.title: Breakwaters - Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Breakwaters on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203180/Breakwaters



The ocean depths are full of mythical Titans, monsters, and treasure.
Only a Breakwater can push back the waters to approach them.
Breakwaters is an adventure survival game with a world scale
ocean sim like you've never seen before.


Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zK83Iun3ln0

Breakwaters Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/breakwatersgame/breakwaters-island-hopping-survival-adventure
